extendedInfo.description: For the girl who loves to dress up like a princess! Create your own princess character. You get to choose her hair, dress, tiara, and more. Who needs a fairy godmother? Dress her in the latest fashions. Get the full version for more features and items.** This popular kids app has millions of downloads around the world. Download and join the fun! **Try our other princess apps - Modern Princess, Mermaid Dress Up, Princess Makeup, and Make My Prince - for more dress up fun!! And for animal lovers, try Sara's Pet Parlour for animal dress up fun.We've added new dresses and items. There is a button now to randomly create princesses for you. And you can now color some of the dresses. ** You can now add sparkles to the outfit by shaking your phone. **Features- Choose a character- Dress her up in the gown of your dreams- Help her do her hair by selecting color and style- Add accessories like tiara and jewelry- Pick out a handbag to go with the outfit- Save your princess character to the gallery to show friends later- Tap on the dice icon and see the different combinations that can be createdHow to Navigate App- Tap on a menu category icon (dress, shoes, etc) to see the different items available- Tap and move finger up or down to see more items - Tap and move finger left or right to see more categories- Tap on X to finish and save your princess or exit
